Scope: this license covers the ORIGINAL content of this modpack repository --
KubeJS scripts (pack/kubejs/), configs (pack/config/, pack/defaultconfigs/),
build/CI scripts (scripts/), documentation, pack manifests/lockfiles
(pack/manifest.json, pack/mods.lock.json, pack/pack.toml), progression data
(pack/progression/), and this repo's own custom Java mods (mods-src/
vppintegration/, mods-src/vppquests/ -- each also carries its own MIT LICENSE
file).

It does NOT cover the third-party Minecraft mods this pack installs/
references (Create, Refined Storage, Apotheosis, etc.) -- each of those
remains under its own upstream license. See THIRD_PARTY.md for the full
per-mod credit/license list.
